Gretchen Seebach, individually, etc., et al., Respondents v. The Metropolitan Elevated Railway Company, et al., Appellants. Decided March 14, 1892. Appeal by defendants from judgment in favor of the plaintiffs entered upon the report of a referee. Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. Sackett & Bennett, for respondents.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., Dugro and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
